methods.description:
Sets the sidebar's contents. The render function is called each tick and must
return a table containing `title` and an array of `lines`.

```luau
player.sidebar:set(function(p)
    return {
        title = "<gold>Stats</gold>",
        lines = { "Name: " .. p.name },
    }
end)
```

